        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n(3 comments)\n\nQuestion, should Serializable interfaces be implemented?   We have some reqs in our apps model to support it drools apps becuase drools primarily.   But not sure if we need them here, don't think will end up in a drools session.   In any case, I want to raise the question, and see what you guys think?",
